HEADWORD: Coregonidae
<hw>Coregonidae</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a natural family of soft-finned
fishes comprising the freshwater whitefishes; formerly included in the
family <fam>Salmonidae</fam>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> family <fam>Coregonidae</fam>.</syn>⟦br⟧
